author: @rebeckaroy6790
text:
When I see a recap like this I think about the months and months of work (and years of experience) that the members and staff pour out in order to create a concert like this.  They give of their life to bring this to reality and I am so so proud of them and just in awe of what they have created together (and with fans).  
This is a beautiful high point that is only reached because they love what they do, they love fans, and they persevere through countless difficulties.  
A thousand thousand times thank you!  Boys, you are amazing and watching this concert was a joy  <3
